/>\n不過其實我覺得唔多唔少關免疫力事 記住早啲訓同食多啲生果 可能會有少少幫助"},{"pid":"88fd2a230ecabef2010b9f4cd11c76bae89bbdd7","tid":678601,"uid":56699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:26:39.000Z","msg":"小學出過一兩年好嚴重，差唔多個個禮拜出，手腳最嚴重，有時生到上臉<br />\n<br />\n之後去驗，發現海鮮，蝦蟹，羊毛，小麥，好似唔知咩蛋白果D過敏，<br />\n戒口，食咗差唔多半年藥好返，再食海鮮果D都無事<br />\n<br />\n大個有時天氣潮濕，捱得夜多抵抗力差，會返發，食藥就好快好返"},{"pid":"77f8808d892f18a0c1aa73b28034ebf44844ebfb","tid":678601,"uid":158906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"461917f3692a1bc1fa1dcaa62132cf2302796abc","tid":678601,"uid":68595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e445307583af134c1064c1ee2f14b63c50c40ac","tid":678601,"uid":32937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T08:47:59.000Z","msg":"每次發就食藥<br />\nlorita loratadine<br />\n每日一粒 需要時服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:37:37.000Z","msg":"其實唔食藥去返冷氣地方等個幾鐘就會退曬<br />\n食藥都唔會阻止到佢出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:29:16.000Z","msg":"我反而係喺凍既地方會出"},{"pid":"2168b90abc5a89c53e65659dfce40f6d06fbae8d","tid":678601,"uid":151786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"073fa38cb4251d6e65cbc2422f8cd37d3664131b","tid":678601,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c21392b3e541d7d113e923852cb80531d5ae39b","tid":678601,"uid":151786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T19:38:01.000Z","msg":"我講下我經歷<br />\n大概中二開始有蕁痲疹，原因不明<br />\n上上下堂會出到咀唇都腫埋<br />\n跟住阿媽帶我樓下睇中醫<br />\n中醫主要俾一劑內服，一劑沖涼<br />\n講下沖涼果part，沖完果下好涼（好似有薄荷咁涼浸浸）<br />\n我記憶中啲藥有昆蟲殻咁上下（而家諗返可能係咸竹蜂）<br />\n食完藥沖完涼好返一排，忘記左維持左幾耐<br />\n<br />\n突然有一日復發，即刻要早退，因為成個人都腫哂咁滯，阿媽又帶我去睇返該名中醫，點知他休假！<br />\n跟住即刻去睇另一個，點知果晚食完藥沖完呢個涼，發得更嚴重，立即阿媽俾急用西藥我食，好辛苦咁捱到第二天，帶埋啲藥渣去見原本個醫師，重點黎了，他說我是熱底人，上個醫師開了些熱底唔可以用既藥材，所以我嚴重左。跟著當然就係佢開藥救返我<br />\n又不知道看了幾多次醫生。就完全好返了。<br />\n不過，睇這位中醫的過程，他有說過，我千萬不能食筍，同埋熱毒野也不要吃。希望我經歷對你有用<br />\n<br />\n其實我都不算完全斷尾，因為我大概每兩三年都會唔知原因咁復發一次，但我可以食西藥幾日就無事。<br />\n<br />\n祝你們早日找到良方斷尾！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T00:35:33.000Z","msg":"求介紹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T06:42:11.000Z","msg":"介唔到嘞，老中醫去向不明<br />\n<br />\n中醫既野，你睇幾次就知夾唔夾<br />\n希望你搵到岩既醫師"},{"pid":"0a416c6378e2c937c32dba41cedefccde21a83fe","tid":678601,"uid":65308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T06:44:35.000Z","msg":"do more exercise<br />\n<br />\nincrease the immune"},{"pid":"76be398eb1f9292f5e0c0881a5371cc6259a71be","tid":678601,"uid":136302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a416c6378e2c937c32dba41cedefccde21a83fe","tid":678601,"uid":65308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T06:44:35.000Z","msg":"do more exercise<br />\n<br />\nincrease the immune"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T21:18:32.000Z","msg":"Day day do exercise already<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2937b68a5a45421d2b548c7ac4e24abf3d1aef","tid":678601,"uid":88999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T22:03:03.000Z","msg":"冬天先會發作<br />\n唔嚴重"},{"pid":"70bb159f0dc3227754c49e863b572f08ff1611a9","tid":678601,"uid":88999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d2937b68a5a45421d2b548c7ac4e24abf3d1aef","tid":678601,"uid":88999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T22:03:03.000Z","msg":"冬天先會發作<br />\n唔嚴重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T22:03:33.000Z","msg":"但夏天一到就輪到濕疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125995fbbfbce14bf2472fcaacea0942945153f3","tid":678601,"uid":120466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T22:07:56.000Z","msg":"我中學個陣好嚴重， 但係一大左做下gym,食多d健康野。除左冬天之外，其他時間都冇野。夏天個陣就算幾熱都唔會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係冬天個陣一熱就會痕。"},{"pid":"9fd1bb910e019aac7357c30cfe891b1e35346a94","tid":678601,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T22:30:26.000Z","msg":"唔好吹風"},{"pid":"b52d56d4b6db7a8769aa1eb911b721ba381d9856","tid":678601,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T23:12:49.000Z","msg":"一熱就出 想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e20b781212d997ee6f2fdb1eb68cc418612497","tid":678601,"uid":8207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:33:05.000Z","msg":"壓力大就出<br />\n熱又出<br />\n<br />\n解決：piriton"},{"pid":"ec93b2b5e46eb8db7cc74e9ab04914e5104f9d28","tid":678601,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:40:15.000Z","msg":"其實中藥係真係可以醫到<br />\n至少有連登巴絲睇<br />\n頭三日藥已經令風疹有明顯分別，痕少左，紅腫減輕好多<br />\n要ko唔係一件難事"},{"pid":"cad9d725821e1c9361bac036678cee5479f3cf2a","tid":678601,"uid":23891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"我生過<br />\n之後發現係蛋白質過多<br />\n果期食太多海鮮引起左<br />\n之黎開始要避蛋白質<br />\n盡量唔好多食海鮮<br />\n同食隻補充藥<br />\n大約大半年左又冇事了"},{"pid":"a2bc462e688644724f3cf9ea825feb17bd1e85b5","tid":678601,"uid":68595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cad9d725821e1c9361bac036678cee5479f3cf2a","tid":678601,"uid":23891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"我生過<br />\n之後發現係蛋白質過多<br />\n果期食太多海鮮引起左<br />\n之黎開始要避蛋白質<br />\n盡量唔好多食海鮮<br />\n同食隻補充藥<br />\n大約大半年左又冇事了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"點發現蛋白質過多？<br />\n我已經好少食海鮮<br />\n食完都唔會即刻出，所以我覺得唔關事，冇乜特別戒"},{"pid":"9a35b031a8d0470a8cfc31198258a6eb59f9bdb0","tid":678601,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:22:28.000Z","msg":"細個試過(12歲咁上下)，持續左我諗有3年<br />\n我老母帶我瘋狂睇中醫，返埋大陸搵d唔係醫院或者診所做既隱世醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後睇好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣真係好痛苦，好驚人見到，好彩仲細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3a4fc82b2e5ffb06245f25fc55417f2d965af0","tid":678601,"uid":29487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"細個個時每隔一排就會發風癩, <br />\n每次老母都係搵佢收藏個D白蘭地濕舊棉花查哂係發作既位置, 忍手唔好R, 一陣就謝哂<br />\n<br />\n大大下就無再生過"},{"pid":"3f5e96be898ae63a50ccdff3bba37e06a7d4390e","tid":678601,"uid":23891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2bc462e688644724f3cf9ea825feb17bd1e85b5","tid":678601,"uid":68595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cad9d725821e1c9361bac036678cee5479f3cf2a","tid":678601,"uid":23891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"我生過<br />\n之後發現係蛋白質過多<br />\n果期食太多海鮮引起左<br />\n之黎開始要避蛋白質<br />\n盡量唔好多食海鮮<br />\n同食隻補充藥<br />\n大約大半年左又冇事了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"點發現蛋白質過多？<br />\n我已經好少食海鮮<br />\n食完都唔會即刻出，所以我覺得唔關事，冇乜特別戒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T09:40:58.000Z","msg":"發之前果排老母好中意買蝦食<br />\n一個星期三四次，都大量<br />\n出事後一食海鮮類就發哂癲咁出<br />\n真係要戒口"},{"pid":"e1b1108efad4172b1f73c4241b8485c5e504f219","tid":678601,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"推返個po上嚟問吓下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時皮膚無乜野 但有時細細力整到啲皮膚或者唔覺意輕輕力抓到後 都會有條痕或者紅腫出現（會有啲痕）但過十幾分鐘就會消失<br />\n有無人都係咁？我見問題不大 所以一直無睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f68cfd61658e2a93394e2a2ccd54dc6a67df34","tid":678601,"uid":65220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1b1108efad4172b1f73c4241b8485c5e504f219","tid":678601,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"推返個po上嚟問吓下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時皮膚無乜野 但有時細細力整到啲皮膚或者唔覺意輕輕力抓到後 都會有條痕或者紅腫出現（會有啲痕）但過十幾分鐘就會消失<br />\n有無人都係咁？我見問題不大 所以一直無睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T16:45:58.000Z","msg":"我都係咁..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十幾歲就開始係咁<br />\n一拎重野/掛係隻手度, 果個位就會生<br />\n或者掂到D塵, 唔乾淨既地方都會<br />\n食左海鮮之後又會生<br />\n<br />\n睇過好多醫生都係開D敏感藥比我, 但我又覺得成日食唔好<br />\n就由佢<br />\n<br />\n我都查過酒..係好似舒服左少少既<br />\n同埋醫生成日話抵抗力好左就會好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過..如果真係好影響平時生活/心情<br />\n都係睇下醫生好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5fdf2235ea746b538591f58f95358dff1e99b7","tid":678601,"uid":68595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:26:08.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過打奧馬珠單抗？ <br />\n成萬蚊一針，仲要連打6 個月，起碼6 萬蚊，唔知真實效果係點？有冇副作用又唔知<br />\n但係好似有個最後嘅希望咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171103/00176_069.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171103%2F00176_069.html&d=epW5akE5sroQ1Eef6JTVggRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=9b90a037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171103/00176_069.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.takungpao.com.hk/paper/q/2015/1002/3198403.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.takungpao.com.hk%2Fpaper%2Fq%2F2015%2F1002%2F3198403.html&d=epW5akE5sroQ1Eef6JTVggRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=4b86f1d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.takungpao.com.hk/paper/q/2015/1002/3198403.html</a>"},{"pid":"545917e3cfe92543e08730327ef7f56a50e4fdaf","tid":678601,"uid":40250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"89d8f72a296d3b0096cb92c45d1af00cf51b2efe","tid":678601,"uid":141448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T20:06:13.000Z","msg":"細個曾經唔知接觸定食錯乜野出過一次<br />\n睇醫生食藥 之後一直無事<br />\n<br />\n相隔幾年 有次游水突然見到手踭有<br />\n之後發現太凍嘅時候就會出<br />\n一去番暖嘅地方就會無事<br />\n已經維持左八年<br />\n一直無睇醫生由得佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:46:06.000Z","msg":"我同你一樣症狀<br />\n依家已經無事<br />\n<br />\n我總結症以下解決方法<br />\n1.）暫時戒食紅肉，奶，呢類蛋白質難消化<br />\n2.）睡眠質素，唔駛訓得耐最緊要訓得好<br />\n3.）沖涼唔好用熱水，怕涷既話每次沖涼都要逐漸減熱，要令身體去適應番溫度<br />\n4.）多游水，多曬太陽，多做帶氧運動。因為遇冷先出風癩，多數血氣唔好。<br />\n5.）如果有脊桂側彎，更加要練背肌。<br />\n6.）多飲水，最好買樽裝礦泉水飲。<br />\n7.）如果係巴打既話，戒J。唔駛全戒，1個月1次係得既。<br />\n<br />\n入面，第3，4，7好重要，因為風癩無濕疹咁難搞，可以用時間俾身體去適應。<br />\n以前去冷氣地方要著冷杉，同掂到涷野都會出風癩。依家乜事都無"},{"pid":"fdde3fdcf54178cd64a3ebcf3110fd1016207748","tid":678601,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"548b9594f12d2ef42db128851daa715b19b37d2a","tid":678601,"uid":68595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e7a446e33af3b316fa51176d47cff1f49b461d91","tid":678601,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/120104_cf2ece1c91316d50f19aaa2b75a25709.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F120104_cf2ece1c91316d50f19aaa2b75a25709.png&h=ac5dabf2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/120117_4053c47d2bfb6d9bb008f40ab7b670bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F120117_4053c47d2bfb6d9bb008f40ab7b670bf.png&h=62969df8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/120130_05872d93fa5befc84f38157edd3f8903.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F120130_05872d93fa5befc84f38157edd3f8903.png&h=41875a03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/120142_d791f70294524110b8801b5f36e90936.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F120142_d791f70294524110b8801b5f36e90936.png&h=450b4c01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/120152_75123de1e8413c9915f61b732deeed3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F